'''''The Tiny Little Dromas''''' is an Event [[Adventure Mission]] from the [[Nice Weather for Dromases]] event.

==Steps==
# Go check out Anaxa's public lecture
# Think of a solution with Hyacine
# Stay with (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) and help it recover!
# Take (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) for a health checkup
# Stay with (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) and help it recover!
# Take (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) for a second health checkup
# Stay with (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) and help it recover!
# Take (Beast of Burden/Mini Dromas/Dromasilla/Dromy/Trailblazer Jr/The Great Chimera/Uranus/Dromasmas) through the final health check

